There certainly have been long and complex discussions on the subject
in this forum, from memory largely conducted between, Chuck, Oerjan,
Michael, Scott and myself. But I do not think anyone has ever published
a Thesis on the subject.

I have read a book entirely devoted to the subject: _Legal Fictions_,
by Lon Fuller. Although not perhaps the easiest book in the world to
read and understand, it does provide a pretty thorough overview of the
subject.

